
Type of beam energy spread BES including beamstrahlung 
is chosen using option KeyFix=xpar(25).
In the code see KarLud_Make, BornV_RhoFoamC.
KeyFix=1 is obsolete,
KeyFix=0 normal/default, no beam spread,
KeyFix=2 beamstrahlung as for ILC, using CIRCE spectra
KeyFix=3,4 for BES according to Patrick Janot distributions
           two equivalent implementations (with/without mapping).

In order to see BES spectrum one may do the following:
    cd ffbench
    cp test0/test0.input_1k_KeyFix=3 test0/test0.input
    make test0-start
    make Plot1
